OL,3,CPrison officer jailed after
OL,4,Cinappropriate relationship with inmate
OL,6,FA prison officer has been jailed after
OL,7,Fshe admitted to having an
OL,8,Finappropriate relationship with an
OL,9,Finmate.
OL,11,FZoe Oldham, 29, of Britannia Street,
OL,12,FBlackburn, who was a prison officer at
OL,13,FHMP Risley, pleaded guilty to
OL,14,Fmisconduct in public office and was
OL,15,Fsentenced to eight months in prison.
OL,17,FOldham admitted to having an
OL,18,Finappropriate relationship with an
OL,19,Finmate at the prison while she was
OL,20,Fworking there.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
