OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1773249076
OL,3,CPrison officer jailed after
OL,4,Cinappropriate relationship with inmate
OL,6,FMerseyside Police said concerns about
OL,7,Fthe nature of their relationship -
OL,8,Fwhich was suspected to be sexual -
OL,9,Fwere first raised in March 2023, when
OL,10,Fstaff noted changes in Oldham's
OL,11,Fbehaviour and appearance.
OL,13,FIntelligence suggested the prisoner
OL,14,Fhad become protective of Oldham, even
OL,15,Fassaulting inmates who had
OL,16,Fdisrespected her.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
