CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1773249076
OL,3,CPrison officer jailed after
OL,4,Cinappropriate relationship with inmate
OL,6,FA court heard how a search of the
OL,7,Fprisoner's cell in March 2023
OL,8,Funcovered a hidden mobile phone inside
OL,9,Fa DVD player, along with paperwork and
OL,10,Fphone numbers. He was moved to a
OL,11,Fdifferent wing.
OL,13,FFurther inquiries revealed more than
OL,14,F1,000 messages exchanged between him
OL,15,Fand a Snapchat account attributed to
OL,16,FOldham, including personal images and
OL,17,Fdeclarations of love.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
