PN,39804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1773249076
OL,3,CPrison officer jailed after
OL,4,Cinappropriate relationship with inmate
OL,6,FIn April 2023, Oldham was searched
OL,7,Fupon entering the prison and appeared
OL,8,Fnervous, although nothing was found at
OL,9,Fthat time. She also attempted to alter
OL,10,Fher work detail to remain close to the
OL,11,Fprisoner.
OL,13,FThe North West Regional Organised
OL,14,FCrime Unit (NWROCU) detained Oldham at
OL,15,FHMP Risley while her home and vehicle
OL,16,Fwere searched.
OL,18,FAt the same time, HMP Wymott staff
OL,19,Fsearched the prisoner's cell, and two
OL,20,Fmobile phones and drugs were found.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
