PN,39805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1773249076
OL,3,CPrison officer jailed after
OL,4,Cinappropriate relationship with inmate
OL,6,FDetective Inspector Brian Morley from
OL,7,Fthe NWROCU's Prison Investigation
OL,8,FTeam, said: "This case highlights the
OL,9,Fdangers posed when individuals in
OL,10,Fpositions of trust engage in
OL,11,Frelationships with prisoners.
OL,13,F"Such conduct compromises the safety
OL,14,Fof staff and inmates and can
OL,15,Ffacilitate further criminality within
OL,16,Fthe prison estate.
OL,18,F"We will continue to work closely with
OL,19,FHM Prison Service and partner agencies
OL,20,Fto identify and disrupt corruption
OL,21,Fwherever it occurs."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
